OL,3,CFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,4,Cwildfires
OL,6,FFirefighters are continuing to control
OL,7,Fa large blaze in Galloway Forest Park
OL,8,Fafter an extreme wildfire warning was
OL,9,Fissued across southern Scotland.
OL,11,FEmergency teams responded to reports
OL,12,Fof a fire at GlenTrool just before
OL,13,Fmidnight on 5 April 2025.
OL,15,FThe Scottish Government called an
OL,16,Femergency meeting to discuss the
OL,17,Fcountry's response to the ongoing
OL,18,Fwildfire in the Galloway area.
