OL,6,F"I am reassured to hear that so far
OL,7,Fthere has been no damage to properties
OL,8,For mature woodland. However, this
OL,9,Fremains an on-going incident and the
OL,10,Fsituation will be reassessed at first
OL,11,Flight.
OL,13,F"Earlier this week the Scottish Fire
OL,14,Fand Rescue Service issued an extreme
OL,15,Fwildfire warning due to the dry
OL,16,Fconditions across much of Scotland.
