OL,3,CFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,4,Cwildfires
OL,6,F"As we continue to see a period of
OL,7,Fwarm and dry weather, it's essential
OL,8,Fthat all of us act responsibly while
OL,9,Fenjoying the outdoors so we can keep
OL,10,Fthe number of wildfires at an absolute
OL,11,Fminimum."
OL,13,FA 'very high' to 'extreme' risk of
OL,14,Fwildfire - the third warning this year
OL,15,F- has been issued by the fire
OL,16,Femergency service from 2 April until
OL,17,Ftoday (Monday 7 April). No casualties
OL,18,Fhave been reported.
