OL,3,CFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,4,Cwildfires
OL,6,FPeople south of the border are being
OL,7,Fto take extra care out in the Cumbrian
OL,8,Fcountryside, as the Cumbria Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service have attended several
OL,10,Fwildfire incidents across the weekend.
OL,12,FPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,13,FDavid Allen says people need to
OL,14,F'follow all local advice'. He said: "I
OL,15,Fwanted to take the opportunity to
OL,16,Fthank our amazing firefighters for the
OL,17,Ftireless work that they've carried out
OL,18,Fover the weekend.
