OL,3,CFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,4,Cwildfires
OL,6,F"There have been a number of
OL,7,Fchallenging fires over the weekend
OL,8,Fwhich they always meet head on. I'm
OL,9,Fincredibly proud of all the staff we
OL,10,Fhave at Cumbria Fire & Rescue Service."
OL,12,FAdvice issued by Cumbria's Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service:
OL,15,FYou can do your bit to protect against
OL,16,Fwildfires by:
OL,18,F- Only have campfires and barbecues in
OL,19,Fallocated areas and always ensure that
OL,20,Fthey are fully extinguished.
