OL,3,CFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,4,Cwildfires
OL,6,F- Never leave your open fire
OL,7,Funattended.
OL,9,F- Dispose of cigarettes and smoking
OL,10,Fmaterials safely.
OL,12,F- If you see a fire outdoors, move to
OL,13,Fa place of safety and report it by
OL,14,Fcalling 999 and do not attempt to
OL,15,Ftackle the fire yourself. Provide as
OL,16,Fmuch information such as the size of
OL,17,Fthe fire, location and terrain.
